## Match System\
Decision: Match is mutual acceptance (not swipe)\
Reason: increases intent quality\
\
## Discovery Feed\
Decision: list-based feed (not swipe cards)\
Reason: supports structured matchmaking + filters\
\
## User Model\
Decision: single account multi-role (player + coach possible)\
Reason: future scalability\
\
## RTL Support\
Decision: RTL supported from Day 1\
Reason: avoid redesign cost later\
